---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="Clinical AI Strategy | AnichLabs OÜ">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Clinical AI Strategy</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Translating clinical needs into technically sound and regulatorily compliant AI product requirements.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-400 mb-3">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Most health-tech teams build AI for clinicians without ever properly understanding clinical reality</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Engineering teams are excellent at building AI systems. But without clinical expertise embedded in the product definition phase, the result is AI that doesn't fit actual workflows, uses clinically inappropriate endpoints, or generates outputs that clinicians don't trust or can't act on. This gap between technical capability and clinical applicability is one of the leading causes of health AI product failure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-10">
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background-color: #EEF2FF; border: 1px solid #C7D2FE;">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #003399">The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Clinical expertise embedded in your AI product strategy from day one</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">AnichLabs OÜ bridges the gap between clinical practice and AI development. Led by a medical doctor with an MSc in Data Analytics, we translate clinical needs into technically sound, regulatorily compliant AI product requirements — so your engineering team builds the right system, not just a technically impressive one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">What's Included</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:stethoscope" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinical Use Case Validation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Assessment of your proposed AI use case against clinical workflows, existing care pathways, and real-world implementation constraints.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:chart-line" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Endpoint & Metric Definition</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Definition of clinically appropriate endpoints, performance metrics, and validation criteria that will satisfy both clinical users and regulatory reviewers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:file-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinical Requirements Specification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Translation of clinical needs into formal product requirements your engineering team can design and build against.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:users-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinician Engagement Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Guidance on how to engage clinical stakeholders, conduct user research, and build clinical advisory relationships that strengthen your product.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:shield-check" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Regulatory Alignment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Ensuring your clinical strategy aligns with EU AI Act, MDR, and clinical guideline requirements from the outset — not after the product is built.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:comment-alt-check" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinical Evidence Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Design of a clinical evaluation and evidence generation plan appropriate for your product class and intended regulatory pathway.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-10 text-center">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Discovery Call (free)</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We discuss your AI product, intended clinical use, and current stage of development to scope the engagement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Clinical Context Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We review your proposed use case against clinical workflows, evidence base, and regulatory requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Requirements & Strategy Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">You receive a clinical requirements specification and strategy document your engineering and regulatory teams can work from.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Ongoing Advisory</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We remain available as clinical advisors throughout development — reviewing outputs, advising on clinical validation, and supporting regulatory submissions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Why do we need clinical expertise if we already have clinical advisors?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">Clinical advisors provide domain knowledge. Clinical AI strategy requires someone who can translate that knowledge into technical requirements, regulatory documentation, and product decisions — a different and rarer skill set.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            At what stage should we engage?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">As early as possible. The earlier clinical expertise is embedded in product definition, the less expensive it is to course-correct. We regularly work with pre-seed teams and early-stage products.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Can you review an AI product we have already built?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">Yes. We conduct clinical and regulatory reviews of existing AI products and identify gaps in clinical appropriateness, evidence, and regulatory readiness.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do you work with specific clinical specialties?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">Our primary background is in general medicine, data-driven clinical decision support, and neurorehabilitation. We work across specialties and bring in clinical network expertise for highly specialised domains.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-20 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Ready to build AI that clinicians will actually use?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call and let's discuss your clinical AI product strategy.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
